project.content:
About

Liquid is the world’s most comprehensive and secure trading platform. Buy and sell Bitcoin, Ethereum, XRP and many other cryptocurrencies with fiat or crypto.

Liquid and ThreeFold

The ThreeFold Token (TFT) has been listed on the Liquid exchange as from May 2020.
project.excerpt: Liquid is the world’s most comprehensive and secure trading platform.
